logue\nto D-branes. The current bosonic setting is the first step toward the dynamics\nof fermionic D-branes (cf. D(11.2): arXiv:1412.0771 [hep-th]) and their\nquantization as fundamental dynamical objects, in parallel to what happened to\nthe theory of fundamental strings during years 1976--1981.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Apr 2017 11:05:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2017-04-12"}
